#. type: Content of: <section><important><itemizedlist><listitem><para>
#: en/content/administration/ticket/priorities.xml:24
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"Ticket:Core::PostMaster:PostmasterDefaultPriority\"> Ticket:"
"Core::Postmaster::PostmasterDefaultPriority</link> - defines the default "
"priority for all incoming emails."
