"server and activate these changes. Then run <command>/usr/bin/"
"mysql_secure_installation</command> and follow the on-screen instructions to "
"set a database root password, remove anonymous access and remove the test "
"database. Lastly, run <command>chkconfig mysqld on</command> in order to "
"make sure mysql is automatically started at server startup time."
msgstr ""

